Goal:
The purpose of this test is to excercise tensor_store with different flavors of it.

Details:
First part - performing tensor_store operations while changing its parameters each time in order to stress as many possible situations:
- Basic test 
- Smaller row sizes (0,1,3)
- Row sweep (0-15)
- Changing start register
- Changing register stride
- Worst latency (stride = 0)
- Smaller stride (0x20)
---------
Second part - Tensor store from scratchpad. After loading  something to scp, we go through different flavors of tensor store from scp:
- Basic tensor store from SCP
- Number of rows sweep 
- Changing the start line
- Changing scp stride

